{"tid":1748074,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港人喺區議會贏過半議席？大數據話係得嘅","createTime":"2019-11-23T13:22:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-23T13:28:44.000Z","uid":279835,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"6e872fa85c8d62033eb85746576bf3c82352ece0","tid":1748074,"uid":279835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T13:22:48.000Z","msg":"30歲以下既年青人, 你地係關鍵呀, 你地有高投票率, 建制點種票都無用. <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n詳細內容睇立場link. <br />\n<br />\n==================================================================<br />\n事實上只要大家唔射票落海，跟返 2016 年超區嘅投票傾向去投，咁樣嘅話連出哂名最難光復嘅觀塘區都係會民主派贏大半數（11 建制，26 民主，3 新增）。而呢度嘅關鍵正正就係 30 歲以下選民。如果 30 歲以下嘅選民嘅投票率係高於全香港平均，就算係返去 2016 年，全港十八區區議會我地都光復到十七個（除咗離島，因為佢地係 10 席民選 8 席當然議員）。<br />\n<br />\n結語<br />\n<br />\n如果想單靠區議會制度同佢嘅職能去改變香港無疑係天方夜譚，但縱觀歷史上成功嘅抗爭（例如 1918 年嘅英屬愛爾蘭大選新芬黨大勝直接引致兩年後嘅獨立戰爭），一味政治潔癖只幻想靠體制外抗爭去改變社會同樣係畫地自限。和勇不分呢四個字講嘅除咗係不割蓆不篤灰外，仲指任何有助勝利嘅方法都會去嘗試，不論當年 G20 登報，8.17 維園百萬流水遊行，舉美國旗定而家區議會選舉。只要行動有成功嘅希望，我地都應該嘗試，願榮光歸香港，大家煲底相見。<br />\n<br />\n光復香港，時代革命！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%BA%E5%96%BA%E5%8D%80%E8%AD%B0%E6%9C%83%E8%B4%8F%E9%81%8E%E5%8D%8A%E8%AD%B0%E5%B8%AD-%E5%A4%A7%E6%95%B8%E6%93%9A%E8%A9%B1%E4%BF%82%E5%BE%97%E5%98%85\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%2596%25BA%25E5%258D%2580%25E8%25AD%25B0%25E6%259C%2583%25E8%25B4%258F%25E9%2581%258E%25E5%258D%258A%25E8%25AD%25B0%25E5%25B8%25AD-%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E6%2595%25B8%25E6%2593%259A%25E8%25A9%25B1%25E4%25BF%2582%25E5%25BE%2597%25E5%2598%2585&d=z%2Bfr9BvhH3rd6UlN4MOb%2FnwvfzOYOHHotQSumXQzHeA%3D&h=43e4e55a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%2596%25BA%25E5%258D%2580%25E8%25AD%25B0%25E6%259C%2583%25E8%25B4%258F%25E9%2581%258E%25E5%258D%258A%25E8%25AD%25B0%25E5%25B8%25AD-%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E6%2595%25B8%25E6%2593%259A%25E8%25A9%25B1%25E4%25BF%2582%25E5%25BE%2597%25E5%2598%2585&h=69dbcfa9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%BA%E5%96%BA%E5%8D%80%E8%AD%B0%E6%9C%83%E8%B4%8F%E9%81%8E%E5%8D%8A%E8%AD%B0%E5%B8%AD-%E5%A4%A7%E6%95%B8%E6%93%9A%E8%A9%B1%E4%BF%82%E5%BE%97%E5%98%85</a>"},{"pid":"18fef34ebb14cea6c5eff5e298a4d5ba4c896ac7","tid":1748074,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T13:27:42.000Z","msg":"go go go"},{"pid":"52107f4f13fc6bb8cb95d791569cb1fdbeb40e78","tid":1748074,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T13:28:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}